<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mstny mjyỷk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mstny mjyỷk wʿạysẖ gẖryb bsẖwq
 lrjwʿk yạ ạ̉gẖly̱ ḥbyb
 shrạn fy ạntẓạrk wbạḥml tẖmạrk wbạsẖhd lḥbk
 wsẖạyl ạlṣlyb
 ạlqrạr- mhmạ ạlgẖrbẗ ṭạlt wạ̉sẖwạkhạ zạdt
 yqyny fy wʿdk bạ̹nk qryb
 wlw ạlạ̉mạny fy ạldnyạ dy kẖạbt htfḍl fy qlby
 ạlrjạ wạlnṣyb
 2- ḥyạty gẖạnyhạ bḥbk rạwyhạ wlạ sẖyʾ yạkẖdny
 ʿn ḥḍnk bʿyd
 dy ạldnyạ wmạ fyhạ lạ ywm htsạwyhạ nẓrẗ
 lsẖkẖṣk yạ nwry ạlwḥyd
 3- rfʿt ʿyny ạ̹lyk yạ fạdy ʿn kl mbạhj qdmhạ
 ạlzmạn
 dạ qlby wḥyạty wkl mạ ly ʿṭyẗ yṣwnhạ fy
 qlby ạlạ̹ymạn</lyrics>
<author>ạ̹yryny bwls, mạykl ạ̹sḥạq</author>
<hymn_number>9310</hymn_number>
</song>